Rockville.Redland, Maryland:
Redland is a census-designated place and an unincorporated area in Montgomery County, Maryland, United States.


== Geography ==
As an unincorporated area, Redland's boundaries are not officially defined. Redland is, however, recognized by the United States Census Bureau as a census-designated place, and by the United States Geological Survey as a populated place located at 39°8′17″N 77°9′19″W (39.137931, -77.155292).
